#
# Grade policy (per task):
#   [11*REPO_INVARIANT]  3+ source corroborated cross-repo (n6+nexus+linter)
#   [10*PASS_LITERATURE] paper-grade with literature citation
#   [10*]                cycle-witness PASS or unconditional lemma
#   [10*FAIL_DOC]        cycle-witness FAIL with falsifier fired (informative)
#   [10]                 atlas-tier observation (cycle-supported)
#   [9]                  conditional / NEAR
#   [7]                  heuristic extracted, single-source
#
# Dedup audit done against:
#   - atlas.n6 main (9,624 entries; @P primitives n,σ,φ,τ,sopfr,J2,μ,M3 NOT
