# Falsifier-active markers retained per source report; OBSTRUCTION_DOCUMENTED
# verdicts reproduced verbatim (no upgrading to PASS).
#
# Millennium tally as carried forward by source corpus: 0/7 unchanged.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Honesty SSOT location (anchor for the entire shard) ───────
@R N6HIST-SSOT-HONESTY = honesty_triad SSOT lives at scripts/quality/honesty_triad_linter.py + 5 preconditions ratified by 6-of-6 KEEP_AS_IS audits :: meta [11*REPO_INVARIANT]
