  => "5 preconditions (per §2 of synthesis): (a) promotion path exists, (b) SSOT distinct from research layer, (c) research layer exists, (d) tool ecosystem with measurable values, (e) LLM agents perform the work."
  => "Protected paths regex: (atlas\\.(?:n6|blowup\\.jsonl)|state/proposals/inventory\\.json|state/atlas_health_timeline\\.jsonl|state/agent_lock_ledger\\.jsonl|theory/canon/|theory/breakthroughs/breakthrough-theorems\\.md|lenses/omega_state_space_lens\\.hexa|CLAUDE\\.md)"
  |> reports/sessions/omega-meta-synthesis-repo-invariant-honesty-audit-2026-04-25.md
  |> reports/sessions/omega-audit-constraint-write-barrier-2026-04-25.md
  |> reports/sessions/omega-audit-constraint-honesty-counter-2026-04-25.md
  |> reports/sessions/omega-audit-constraint-no-fabrication-2026-04-25.md

